"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the IBA's concerns over sporting fairness and fighter safety may even be valid.\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4495, \"end\": 4498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999985969935389, \"rank\": 1.4030083477881026e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sporting fairness\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4532}, {\"ngram\": \"fighter safety\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a complicated, sensitive topic, and conversations over fairness and safety are worth having.\", \"from\": 4571, \"to\": 4671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a complicated, sensitive topic\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4609}, {\"ngram\": \"conversations\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"fairness\", \"from\": 4634, \"to\": 4642}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The issue is: almost no one is having these conversations, because the narratives around Khelif and Lin's Olympic campaigns have been hijacked, and dragged into the mire of wider culture wars.\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The issue\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4681}, {\"ngram\": \"almost no one\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4699}, {\"ngram\": \"these conversations\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4729}, {\"ngram\": \"the narratives\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4753}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4767}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin's Olympic campaigns\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4795}, {\"ngram\": \"the mire\", \"from\": 4833, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"wider culture wars\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And among the verbal grenades, lobbed haphazardly over battle lines, are entirely unfounded allegations that Khelif is a transgender athlete.\", \"from\": 4865, \"to\": 5006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the verbal grenades\", \"from\": 4875, \"to\": 4894}, {\"ngram\": \"battle lines\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 4932}, {\"ngram\": \"entirely unfounded allegations\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 4968}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 4980}, {\"ngram\": \"a transgender athlete\", \"from\": 4984, \"to\": 5005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is despite Khelif having been, to all knowledge, born and raised as a woman and never having identified as transgender or intersex.\", \"from\": 5008, \"to\": 5144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5030}, {\"ngram\": \"all knowledge\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5131}, {\"ngram\": \"intersex\", \"from\": 5135, \"to\": 5143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same applies to Lin.\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5165, \"to\": 5168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And somewhere in here lies the fact, trivial as it may seem, that Khelif and Lin have lost to fellow women a combined 23 times - and that both competed at the Tokyo Games without winning medals.\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5205}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5236, \"to\": 5242}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5250}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow women\", \"from\": 5264, \"to\": 5276}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5340}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In any case, the most vicious region of this ever-spinning cyclone has seen Khelif and Lin wrongly accused of being men, fighting women.\", \"from\": 5366, \"to\": 5502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any case\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5377}, {\"ngram\": \"the most vicious region\", \"from\": 5379, \"to\": 5402}, {\"ngram\": \"this ever-spinning cyclone\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5432}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5448}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5456}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5485}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among those spreading this sentiment wereX owner Elon MuskandHarry Potterauthor JK Rowling.\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5583, \"end\": 5593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sentiment\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was always likely that the storm would intensify if either boxer secured a medal, and that a downburst could accompany a gold medal.\", \"from\": 5596, \"to\": 5735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the storm\", \"from\": 5626, \"to\": 5635}, {\"ngram\": \"either boxer\", \"from\": 5655, \"to\": 5667}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 5676, \"to\": 5683}, {\"ngram\": \"a downburst\", \"from\": 5694, \"to\": 5705}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 5722, \"to\": 5734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has fought twice since Carini's withdrawal,which was followed by an apology from the Italian.\", \"from\": 5737, \"to\": 5837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5767, \"end\": 5773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999997689883, \"rank\": 2.311171078309867e-10, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\":